We have 15 minutesand you have some cool stuffto show us.

50:41.995 --> 50:44.258
- Oh, yeah.

50:47.131 --> 50:48.741
I want you to join Devs.

50:51.396 --> 50:52.614
What is Devs?

50:55.574 --> 50:57.924
It's the most beautiful thingI've ever seen.

51:05.366 --> 51:06.802
I'm gonna miss you so much,

51:06.846 --> 51:08.935
but we can speak on the computerso you'll see my face.

51:08.978 --> 51:11.024
But we won't be able
to touch you.

51:11.068 --> 51:12.373
Hey, look.
You'll still have me.

51:12.417 --> 51:15.333
-Just you?-Yes. Just-- Your father. Hi.

51:22.383 --> 51:24.429
Do I just knock, or what?
What do you think?

51:26.300 --> 51:28.302
I feel like
they're not ever gonna...

51:30.261 --> 51:32.263
Why are you wearing
your sunglasses inside?

