Okay. You're welcome.

51:41.402 --> 51:43.317
I feel like that did nothing
for my career.

51:52.413 --> 51:53.545
Oh, damn!

52:03.381 --> 52:05.687
They had come
highly recommended

52:05.818 --> 52:09.343
by a mutual vampire
associate of ours,

52:09.474 --> 52:11.780
but nevertheless,
I found it prudent

52:11.824 --> 52:14.043
-to run the traditional
credit checks...

